abstract: The coffee chain reported profits of $626.7 million, and its revenue grew 17.5 percent, to $4.9 billion.

lead_paragraph: The global obsession with coffee shows no signs of abating, propelling sales and profits at the world’s most ubiquitous coffee chain, Starbucks.
